<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="AllGenres_style.css" />
    <link rel="icon" href="images/open-book.png" />
    <title><%=title%></title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="nav_bar">
      <nav>
        <a href="Home"
          ><img src="images/logo.jpg" alt="Bookly Logo" class="nav_logo"
        /></a>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="Home">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="Genres">Genres</a></li>
          <li><a href="Recommendations">Recommendations</a></li>
          <li><a href="personalbooks"><%=name%></a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="quote">
      <h1>
        “People with a grudge against the world are always dangerous. They seem
        to think life owes them something.”
      </h1>
      <h3>
        -Agatha Christie- <br />
        <i>A Murder Is Announced</i>
      </h3>
    </div>

    <hr />

    <div class="main-div">
      <h4>Featured Book:</h4>
      <div class="book-info">
        <a
          href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/59344312-verity"
          target="_blank"
        >
          <img src="images/verity.jpg" alt="Verity"
        /></a>
        <div class="book-desc">
          <h2>Verity</h2>
          <p>
            Lowen Ashleigh is a struggling writer on the brink of financial ruin
            when she accepts the job offer of a lifetime. Jeremy Crawford,
            husband of bestselling author Verity Crawford, has hired Lowen to
            complete the remaining books in a successful series his injured wife
            is unable to finish. Watch their story unfold when incomprehensible
            things happen around them.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr />

    <div class="main-div">
      <h4>Signs Your Next Read Should be Thriller:</h4>
      <div class="signs">
        <div class="sign">
          <img src="images/thriller.png" alt="suspense" />
          <p>You Like Suspense</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sign">
          <img src="images/scared.png" alt="scared" />
          <p>You're not Easily Scared</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sign">
          <img src="images/adrenaline.png" alt="adrenaline" />
          <p>You're an Adrenaline Junkie</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <img src="images/logo.jpg" alt="Bookly Logo" class="footer-logo" />
      <p>Our goal at Bookly is to help you decide on your next read.</p>
      <p>Follow us for more:</p>
      <div class="socials">
        <a
          href="https://www.facebook.com/mariajane.wehbe.9"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer noopener"
          title="Facebook"
          ><img src="images/facebook-brands.svg" alt="Facebook"
        /></a>
        <a
          href="https://www.instagram.com/mariajanewehbe"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer noopener"
          title="Instagram"
          ><img src="images/instagram-brands.svg" alt="Instagram"
        /></a>
        <a
          href="https://twitter.com/mariajane_wehbe"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer noopener"
          title="Twitter"
          ><img src="images/twitter-square-brands.svg" alt="Twitter"
        /></a>
        <a
          href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/37042627-maria-jane"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer noopener"
          title="Goodreads"
          ><img src="images/goodreads-brands.svg" alt="Goodreads"
        /></a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
